://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwitter4HK&d=xz9%2BKahtnlDLfwjNDOwuFP8K46P7%2BXxs1F7ZCKkfkQw%3D&h=215d3078\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/twitter4HK</a><br />\n<br />\n[置頂] 建議9月8日百萬人大遊行/集會，<br />\n請求美國國會通過人權及民主法案<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1530650\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1530650</a><br />\n<br />\n901 機場測試係成功<br />\n辛苦曬行左20公里既手足 勿被帶風向<br />\n<br />\n908 我希望美國巴絲手足都有遊行<br />\n聲援香港同埋同要請求美國國會通過人權法!<br />\n<br />\n908 建議：<br />\n-大量英文文宣/紙牌<br />\n-高舉大量美國議員大頭相<br />\n-高舉大量國旗<br />\n-唔建議勇武，因為主題涉及美國<br />\n(另一原因係 廢時佢又區區有狗搜身兼 補充文具需時又珍貴)<br />\n-領事館門前唱國歌<br />\n<br />\n無人申請不反 都要照上街<br />\n需要文宣制圖 然後我幫你宣傳<br />\n由今日開始宣! 908照上街!<br />\n<br />\n建議內容copy某位巴打既<br />\n9月我要照上街<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"233b1e7060d9dcd79adbe1c1268dd13683c6bff3","tid":1534224,"uid":159216,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:48:24.000Z","msg":"香港鋪頭都係得一兩間敢做<br />\n真係無咩說服力叫外國響應 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86ef60f446b9cc14e7d77ef382aa9a4f23d9a568","tid":1534224,"uid":31501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"233b1e7060d9dcd79adbe1c1268dd13683c6bff3","tid":1534224,"uid":159216,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:48:24.000Z","msg":"香港鋪頭都係得一兩間敢做<br />\n真係無咩說服力叫外國響應 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:49:47.000Z","msg":"可以用個一兩間做引例<br />\n外國咁做應該風險低過香港"},{"pid":"4c3cb229c7776c3d094889f617ceb9223e9c5565","tid":1534224,"uid":31501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:56:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"909454ec17c765f90c0d01efc5533ef0b4ec8879","tid":1534224,"uid":78651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:56:51.000Z","msg":"加辣，要美國國會sanction埋警隊及其成員"},{"pid":"0c6d8feec44dc9971952ce7b677373f5d7d0771c","t